  <brief_title>Multicenter, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo Controlled, Efficacy Study on the Effects of Tolvaptan on Left Ventricular Dilatation in Congestive Heart Failure Patients</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Otsuka Pharmaceutical Development &amp; Commercialization, Inc.</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Otsuka Pharmaceutical Development &amp; Commercialization, Inc.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to study the effects of tolvaptan on the size and function of
      the left heart chamber (ventricle) in patients with congestive heart failure (CHF)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
